reviewtext: This cable was received neatly coiled with twist-ties in a retail package. The connectors, which are already applied, will not loosen over time like manually pinned out cables will have a special design to protect the security clip from breaking off. This allows the RJ45 connectors to fit firmly in place and not fall out of the network port.Belkin is a recognized brand for premium cables. Even though this is a name brand cable, the price was comparable to other similar cables making this purchase a clear best choice.
summary: Reliable Name Brand at a Great Price
